  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>·      Provide day-to-day administrative support including answering <br />       calls, filing, data entry, and document management</p><p>·      Prepare quotations, delivery orders, invoices, purchase orders, <br />       and claims</p><p>·      Maintain proper documentation and filing systems</p><p>·      Liaise with suppliers, clients, engineers, and internal staff</p><p>·      Support engineers and management as required</p><p>·      Perform other administrative and basic accounting duties as     <br />       assigned</p><p><strong>Requirements : </strong></p><p>·      Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level / NITEC / Diploma</p><p>·      At least 1 year of relevant administrative experience <br />       (engineering industry experience is an advantage)</p><p>·      Proficient in MS Office</p><p>·      Good communication and organisational skills</p><p>·      Meticulous, detail-oriented, and positive attitude</p><p>·      Able to multitask and work independently or in a team<br /><br />·      Able to start work immediately<br /><br />Singaporeans / PRs preferred</p><p>Working Hours: Monday to Friday, 8:30am – 5:30pm</p><p>How to Apply:</p><p>Email your resume to hr@synergexeng.com</p><p>(Only shortlisted candidates will be notified)</p>",
